headline: Milestone in Mascoutah: Regions Banker Celebrates 60 Years at the Same Branch
summary: Several Regions Bank leaders drop in to celebrate Mary Lou Schlueter for her extraordinary record of customer service. By Wayne Thompson NORTHAMPTON, MA / ACCESS Newswire / June 27, 2025 / Mary Lou Schlueter made the same three-block trip from home ...
